      </span>
				<p>See <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/ot/judg/13.7?lang=eng#6" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Judges 13:7</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/nt/luke/1.15?lang=eng#14" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Luke 1:15</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/89.5,7-9?lang=eng#4" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 89:5, 7&ndash;9</a>.</p>
