			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-00605_000_039"><a name="-00605_000_039">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote41-00605_000_039">41.</a>
      </span>
				<p>See <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/nt/john/13.15?lang=eng#14" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">John 13:15</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/nt/1-tim/4.12?lang=eng#11" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">1 Timothy 4:12</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/nt/1-pet/2.21?lang=eng#20" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">1 Peter 2:21</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/31.16?lang=eng#15" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">2 Nephi 31:16</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/18.16?lang=eng#15" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">3 Nephi 18:16</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/morm/7.10?lang=eng#9" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Mormon 7:10</a>.</p>
